title: The Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show Podcast
itunes:title: The Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show Podcast
description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 2: Trump shames Kamala Harris into visiting the border. Flashback to Harris "I haven't been to Europe" moment with Lester Holt. Clay wonders if 2008 Obama could be elected in today's Democrat Party. Buck describes his visit to the border. Bernie Sanders is mad that GOP stopped the Democrat power grab voting bill, unleashes on Manchin and Sinema for saving the filibuster. Buck does his spot-on Bernie impression.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
